INSERT INTO artisans VALUES(414,'PABAFUR','','Pink And Blue Addicts Fursuits','','Thanks for checking me out! I am a fursuit maker based in lower Michigan, that''s been making fursuits since summer 2019. I decided that I wanted to become a fursuit maker in 2020, so I opened in September 2020. Every suit I make are not casted in bases, so if you have a character that just quite doesn''t look like the rest of the suits you see on my website, I''d be a great choice for you!','2019-05','US','Michigan','',replace('Artistic liberty commissions\nPremades\nStandard commissions','\n',char(10)),'Toony',replace('Handpaws (as parts/separate)\nHead (as parts/separate)\nMini partial (head + handpaws + tail)\nTails (as parts/separate)','\n',char(10)),replace('Exchangeable hairs\nExchangeable tongues\nFollow-me eyes','\n',char(10)),'','100% Upfront, or payment plan created by commissioner. No payment to reserve, shipping saved for last.',replace('Canines\nCervine\nFelines','\n',char(10)),replace('Equines\nBirds\nAmphibian\nScalies','\n',char(10)),'English','','FEEDBACK','E-MAIL','E-MAIL: pink***********uits@gm*****om','','','Plushies','Most of the time I do standard commissions, but I''m willing to do artistic liberty anytime.','I only do foam heads (I don''t use casts or molds either)','Expecting digitigrade bodysuits and feet paws by summer time of 2021!','Exchangeable hairs are considered an extra feature. Exchangeable tongues and follow-me eyes are given to every suit (except for characters that are "squinting").',replace('Debit (PayPal)\nCredit (PayPal)\nPayPal Balance (PayPal)','\n',char(10)),'USD','I haven''t "completed" a suit that is in the cervine category, I made a foam head by mistake. Willing to make a deer suit though!');
